
Windows(2k25):
    -> download via torent 2 rar files.
    -> unzip part-1 only, it will use part-2 and create a directory.
    -> open the directory and run exe with admin privilages
    -> if the game crash and do not start properly then remove crashbin directory.
    -> recommended settings : 720p and 30fps, no-shadow, audiance density.  



Windows(2k19):
    -> download via torent 9 rar files.
    -> unzip part-1 only, it will use all parts and create a directory.
    -> open the directory and mount iso file inside.
    -> run exe file inside iso. it will install the game.


